    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'High above the world, the floating sky kingdom of Aetheris was guarded
    by dragon clans and sustained by a sacred fire known as the Eternal Ember.

    When
    the ember burned bright, the skies were calm, the temples stood strong, and the
    dragon realm prospered.


    But from the volcanic abyss rose a corrupted brood
    of dragons, the Shadow Drakes.

    Twisted by darkness and hunger, they attacked
    the kingdom, shattered the sky gates, and set the cloud temples ablaze.

    Aetheris
    fell into ruin.


    In the final moments before the capital collapsed, the
    elders entrusted the last surviving spark of the Eternal Ember to a young dragon
    hatchling, ypu.

    Now you must fly through broken gates, collapsing ruins,
    and burning skies while hunted by Shadow Drakes determined to extinguish the
    ember forever.


    To survive, you weave through dangerous openings, collect
    glowing ember hearts to restore strength, and unleash fire breath to defeat enemy
    dragons.

    As the journey continues, the skies grow faster and deadlier.


    You
    have only three lives to protect the final flame.

    If the ember survives,
    Aetheris may rise again.


    If it is lost, the sky kingdom will become nothing
    but ash.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
